 magnetic state which can be described using a propagation\nvector, (1/4, 1/4, 0). Upon Mg-dilution at $x \\geq$0.1, the long-range ordered\nmagnetism is destroyed. The present results should motivate an investigation of\nmagnetic excitations in this low-dimensional anisotropic magnet.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2019 05:18:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-05"}
