s an additional\nadvantage: It can be statically condensed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2019 00:56:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Dec 2019 20:50:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-16"}
